280
00:09:37.010 --> 00:09:38.470
What?!

281
00:09:38.470 --> 00:09:40.850
That's the situation?!

282
00:09:41.190 --> 00:09:43.980
Yeah. Even with all
the Marines in the world

283
00:09:43.980 --> 00:09:47.270
it's too much to handle.

284
00:09:44.020 --> 00:09:47.270
Captain Koby
Marine Headquarters
Member of SWORD

285
00:09:47.270 --> 00:09:49.820
So just as we planned,

286
00:09:49.820 --> 00:09:53.030
the Marines won't get involved
with what's going on over there.

287
00:09:53.030 --> 00:09:54.870
They don't have enough manpower.

288
00:09:54.870 --> 00:09:56.370
That's fine.

289
00:09:56.370 --> 00:09:59.200
Wano isn't affiliated with
the World Government.

290
00:09:59.660 --> 00:10:03.790
Now, about Big Mom arriving at Onigashima...

291
00:10:03.790 --> 00:10:04.500
Yes.

292
00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:08.710
Kaido and Big Mom
have been at odds for so long

293
00:10:08.710 --> 00:10:12.090
that the Marines are hoping those
two pirates will ruin each other.

294
00:10:12.090 --> 00:10:13.630
Yeah, I guess.

295
00:10:13.630 --> 00:10:18.850
As we expected, Kaido and Big Mom
were at each other's throats...

296
00:10:20.220 --> 00:10:22.020
but now they've joined hands!

297
00:10:24.230 --> 00:10:28.270
Wh-Wh-Wh-What do you mean?!

298
00:10:32.110 --> 00:10:35.870
As for Straw Hat Luffy,
there's been no word of a breakout.

299
00:10:36.490 --> 00:10:38.740
The situation is at a standstill.

300
00:10:38.740 --> 00:10:41.120
There's also one more unpleasant thing.

301
00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:44.080
I saw Cipher Pol 0 in the capital the other day.

302
00:10:44.080 --> 00:10:46.210
What?! Why are they in Wano?!

303
00:10:47.380 --> 00:10:49.380
I hope I'm wrong,

304
00:10:49.750 --> 00:10:52.590
but it must mean the World Government

305
00:10:52.590 --> 00:10:56.180
is doing business with Wano,
a country ruled by a pirate.

306
00:10:58.300 --> 00:11:00.010
When I found out,

307
00:11:00.510 --> 00:11:01.180
I was stunned for a few minutes.

308
00:11:01.180 --> 00:11:03.430
I was stunned for a few minutes.

309
00:11:13.280 --> 00:11:15.910
By the way, where are you now?

310
00:11:15.910 --> 00:11:16.610
Right.

311
00:11:17.410 --> 00:11:20.950
We're heading toward the Isle of Women...

312
00:11:25.500 --> 00:11:28.080
to capture Pirate Empress Boa Hancock!

313
00:11:28.960 --> 00:11:29.790
Oh, my...

314
00:11:30.420 --> 00:11:33.840
Those ships coming toward us
over the Calm Belt...

315
00:11:33.840 --> 00:11:35.630
Is that a Marine fleet?!

316
00:11:36.590 --> 00:11:38.680
Marguerite!

317
00:11:38.680 --> 00:11:41.560
What's going to happen?!

318
00:11:43.810 --> 00:11:46.770
The news spread all around the world.

319
00:11:47.770 --> 00:11:50.480
They should have done this a long time ago!

320
00:11:50.480 --> 00:11:53.110
It was a mistake to team up with pirates...

321
00:11:53.780 --> 00:11:54.860
They're evil!

322
00:11:55.530 --> 00:11:58.280
For those who think all pirates are bad...

323
00:12:00.370 --> 00:12:03.200
Those government dogs will finally go away!

324
00:12:03.580 --> 00:12:07.080
Screw that Pirate Empress,
Hawk Eye, and Clown!

325
00:12:07.080 --> 00:12:10.210
They're nothing but looters!

326
00:12:11.460 --> 00:12:15.300
...and for those who hate looters,
it's good news.

327
00:12:15.630 --> 00:12:19.800
But I thought they did great
in the Summit War!

328
00:12:20.640 --> 00:12:22.220
That's what they decided?!

329
00:12:22.760 --> 00:12:25.140
The Marines are ready
to take immediate action.

330
00:12:25.140 --> 00:12:26.430
Is this really wise?

331
00:12:26.430 --> 00:12:30.100
They were one of the world's
three great powers!

332
00:12:30.100 --> 00:12:33.730
For those who knew of
their feats in the Summit War,

333
00:12:33.730 --> 00:12:38.490
and those who were concerned about disrupting
the balance of the three great powers,

334
00:12:38.490 --> 00:12:40.990
it was truly an alarming situation.

335
00:12:43.870 --> 00:12:49.540
The news story from the latest Reverie
that stunned people across the world the most...

336
00:12:50.120 --> 00:12:51.040
was...

337
00:12:52.630 --> 00:12:54.210
the abolition...

338
00:12:54.840 --> 00:12:56.340
of the Seven Warlords system!

339
00:12:57.880 --> 00:13:02.760
The Seven Warlords of the Sea were pirates
officially recognized by the government.

340
00:13:02.760 --> 00:13:05.180
While they were allowed to pillage,

341
00:13:05.180 --> 00:13:10.100
the government used them
as deterrents against other pirates.

342
00:13:10.100 --> 00:13:15.730
The roster of the Seven Warlords
has changed over time.

343
00:13:22.070 --> 00:13:23.410
Crocodile.

344
00:13:23.950 --> 00:13:28.870
He clashed with the Straw Hats
over the Kingdom of Alabasta.

345
00:13:28.870 --> 00:13:31.750
He was trying to take over the kingdom

346
00:13:31.750 --> 00:13:35.840
but was ultimately defeated by Luffy
and expelled from the Seven Warlords.

347
00:13:36.750 --> 00:13:40.170
The man who replaced Crocodile
and joined the Seven Warlords...

348
00:13:40.170 --> 00:13:42.430
was Marshall D. Teach.

349
00:13:42.430 --> 00:13:48.890
However, he announced his resignation
after achieving his goal.

350
00:13:50.180 --> 00:13:52.140
Jinbe, Knight of the Sea,

351
00:13:52.140 --> 00:13:54.940
opposed the Summit War and grew
disdainful of the Marines.

352
00:13:55.650 --> 00:13:58.610
He, too, declared his resignation.

353
00:14:01.860 --> 00:14:03.700
Gecko Moria.

354
00:14:03.700 --> 00:14:10.000
This man who had once clashed with the Straw Hats
was also called to the Summit War.

355
00:14:11.160 --> 00:14:12.120
However...

356
00:14:13.540 --> 00:14:17.800
just after the war, an order for an ambush
came from high up in the government,

357
00:14:17.800 --> 00:14:19.630
and he was expelled.

358
00:14:20.550 --> 00:14:23.510
Heavenly Demon Donquixote Doflamingo.

359
00:14:25.180 --> 00:14:28.180
All while governing Dressrosa as its king,

360
00:14:28.180 --> 00:14:33.770
he trafficked an artificial devil fruit, SMILE,
as an influential underground broker.

361
00:14:34.270 --> 00:14:35.440
However...

362
00:14:36.480 --> 00:14:39.770
he lost the kingdom in a struggle
against Luffy's alliance,

363
00:14:39.770 --> 00:14:41.990
and his title of Warlord was revoked.

364
00:14:42.440 --> 00:14:45.160
And finally, Trafalgar Law.

365
00:14:45.160 --> 00:14:49.120
He allied himself with the Straw Hats
to take down Doflamingo...

366
00:14:49.790 --> 00:14:52.250
and was stripped of his title.

367
00:14:53.250 --> 00:14:56.630
The four pirates who reign supreme
as if they're emperors:

368
00:14:58.250 --> 00:14:59.420
the Four Emperors.

369
00:15:00.340 --> 00:15:03.220
And trying to contain them:
Marine Headquarters.

370
00:15:03.720 --> 00:15:06.550
Last but not least:
The Seven Warlords of the Sea.

