536
00:15:13.480 --> 00:15:16.690
two kings had suffered terribly
at the hands of Warlords:

537
00:15:16.690 --> 00:15:20.020
King Nefertari Cobra
of the Kingdom of Alabasta,

538
00:15:20.610 --> 00:15:23.780
and Riku Doldo III
of the Kingdom of Dressrosa.

539
00:15:23.780 --> 00:15:26.860
They fought for the abolition
of the Seven Warlords system.

540
00:15:27.530 --> 00:15:31.080
Then, after a heated debate at the Reverie,

541
00:15:31.080 --> 00:15:35.460
a large majority supported
the proposition, and it passed.

542
00:15:36.710 --> 00:15:42.300
Therefore, the Seven Warlords of the Sea
will automatically be stripped of all their rights,

543
00:15:42.300 --> 00:15:46.180
and their connection with
the World Government will hereby be cut off.

544
00:15:46.180 --> 00:15:47.010
That means...!

545
00:15:47.010 --> 00:15:50.470
Empty Bluffs Island
New World

546
00:15:47.890 --> 00:15:49.260
Buggy,

547
00:15:49.260 --> 00:15:53.270
you're just another pirate!

548
00:15:54.140 --> 00:15:56.390
That's no fair, you assholes!

549
00:15:56.390 --> 00:16:01.440
A decision was made without telling us,
and since we're no longer useful, you arrest us?!

550
00:16:01.440 --> 00:16:03.650
You have no sense of justice whatsoever!

551
00:16:03.650 --> 00:16:08.240
Whether Crocodile and Doflamingo
outsmarted you is none of my business!

552
00:16:08.240 --> 00:16:11.240
Don't take it out on me!

553
00:16:11.240 --> 00:16:13.830
They've got the whole coast surrounded!

554
00:16:14.330 --> 00:16:15.870
What should we do?

555
00:16:16.910 --> 00:16:20.790
My entire life's plan is going to the dogs!

556
00:16:21.290 --> 00:16:22.250
Oh?

557
00:16:22.290 --> 00:16:27.720
An Island
in the New World

558
00:16:22.630 --> 00:16:25.920
The Marines should be on our side,
but they've surrounded us!

559
00:16:25.920 --> 00:16:27.720
What should we do, Mommy?!

560
00:16:28.300 --> 00:16:30.180
Mommy!

561
00:16:31.640 --> 00:16:35.060
The Ruins of the Muggy Kingdom
Gloom Island

562
00:16:31.800 --> 00:16:33.560
Surrender yourself now,

563
00:16:33.560 --> 00:16:35.060
Hawk Eye Mihawk!

564
00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:37.680
Surrender yourself now!

565
00:16:39.140 --> 00:16:42.150
The Isle of Women
Amazon Lily

566
00:16:39.390 --> 00:16:42.150
Snyake Princess, we have a problem!

567
00:16:42.150 --> 00:16:46.440
Your title of Warlord has been stripped away!

568
00:16:47.110 --> 00:16:48.360
Elder Nyon!

569
00:16:48.360 --> 00:16:50.320
There are Marine ships off the coast!

570
00:16:50.320 --> 00:16:51.530
What?!

571
00:16:51.530 --> 00:16:54.160
They've already gone into action?!

572
00:16:55.160 --> 00:16:56.580
Don't panic!

573
00:16:57.910 --> 00:16:59.210
Snyake Princess!

574
00:16:59.540 --> 00:17:01.750
They've obviously forgotten something...

575
00:17:03.460 --> 00:17:04.710
don't you think?

576
00:17:05.170 --> 00:17:07.970
This is no good, President Buggy!

577
00:17:07.970 --> 00:17:09.380
Should we run?!

578
00:17:10.010 --> 00:17:14.050
Of course not! We'll show them a flashy fight!

579
00:17:18.680 --> 00:17:23.900
Show some guts, you sad sacks!

580
00:17:25.190 --> 00:17:27.780
– That's our President Buggy!
– That's our President Buggy!

